(modularity-policy
 max-source-lines: 800
 max-test-lines: 1000
 max-test-cases: 24
 max-test-definition-span: 260
 explanation: "Harness parser and policy owners carry parser-fact aggregation, typed-ledger comments, and agent repair detail payloads. Source owners stay below the hard 1000-line cap and must split once effective owner lines exceed 800; package-local t/ owners are capped at 1000.")
